{"tid":1343703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［心靈加油站］被最近事件搞到心力交瘁，精神不振既巴絲","createTime":"2019-07-21T19:16:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T01:11:33.000Z","uid":123713,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"38ac3f86c8c8cfd69db5a5169e5722690638958a","tid":1343703,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:16:06.000Z","msg":"由69開始 每星期至少一次既行動<br />\n原本以為612已經夠離譜<br />\n結果714沙田新城市同721元朗就愈演愈on9<br />\n<br />\n成件事每個細節都掀動住每一個真香港人既情緒<br />\n林鄭既嘴臉、高官即無能無恥、警察無法無天、甚至政警黑合作打市民<br />\n<br />\n無錯 真係好嬲 嬲到講撚晒粗口 甚至想郁手開拖<br />\n無時無刻拎住手機，係連登，TG同直播之間來回<br />\n好驚下一秒其他手足會出事<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但呢種高強度既精神崩緊<br />\n令到身邊唔少朋友出現：<br />\n頭痛 胃痛 冇胃口 失眠 專注下力降 甚至抑鬱</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">如果大家發現自己有以上任何症狀<br />\n我建議大家先放低電話 唔好比自己繼續loop落去<br />\n先好好休息 面對自己既情緒 覺知自己既心情 <br />\n整頓好之後 （可能只係訓一覺）<br />\n再回歸戰線</span></span>"},{"pid":"e1bf3b4cae6e84f84a3fb431b63d05cc07137149","tid":1343703,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:22:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf721d64469b428c6048a37c83e9906ef2a8eb7c","tid":1343703,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:28:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7917ef7b9106b9f793a8acf144b09812f1d4afba","tid":1343703,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:55:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8066cd175353e00ee17950648485f6be8003beda","tid":1343703,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:05:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afc04fc68c21b2cdfac537bec5d020e1f5636b78","tid":1343703,"uid":284624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:08:50.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n如果好攰就休息一下再打過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">頂住啊，關鍵時期少你一個就係唔得！</span><br />\n]"},{"pid":"dfa0e2f9d1f47a133e2183081c047b2ac4dbd369","tid":1343703,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:53:35.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n自己都就黎痴線<br />\n記住逼自己抖下"},{"pid":"48cd599cc6f3239e24b9c2232e6fe3c506937b1c","tid":1343703,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:29:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d1b2f34f7688b063ad5cd0eca9454ff6d295785","tid":1343703,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:31:19.000Z","msg":"何君堯中環皇后大道中5號衡怡大廈18樓律師樓好太平<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1349881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1349881</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7883c2423f5d1d81de355f18fde5ee597fd8b4c1","tid":1343703,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:35:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ceb316fef0c4e9e37e05556d1afedebbdda80d2","tid":1343703,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:54:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2227ea947b69ec0fea03713e2f0f457ea044be4","tid":1343703,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:33:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84a6b2d1c4e03c3f313627fdb6f3e63330a83bab","tid":1343703,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:58:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99ba7257e565cdc166a2daffd28326fbba537e82","tid":1343703,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:22:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc179031f333b0677220fb6817059daeaf165b1a","tid":1343703,"uid":285842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:23:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c85660f776528112cefb26c64c8e00a61768df52","tid":1343703,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:35:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"165bd8edee3450bfabb3265332cf0b779155b742","tid":1343703,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:59:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"p